'''Angela Phillips''', also known as '''Angela P. Wade''', is a writer, costume maker and doll artist.

==Biography==
Angela lives in [[Wikipedia:Newport News|Newport News]], [[Wikipedia:Virginia|Virginia]]. Angela married John Wade on [[July 24]], [[1999]]. She gave birth to Samuel J. Wade on [[August 18]], [[2003]] and Elizabeth B. Wade on [[February 14]], [[2006]].

